<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Document signé</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#f4f4f5;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,sans-serif;">
  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#f4f4f5;padding:32px 16px;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center">
        <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="max-width:560px;background:#ffffff;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid #e4e4e7;">
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:28px 32px 8px;">
              <p style="margin:0;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.04em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#71717a;">Atome</p>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:8px 32px 24px;">
              <h1 style="margin:0 0 16px;font-size:22px;font-weight:600;color:#18181b;line-height:1.35;">
                Document signé
              </h1>
              <p style="margin:0 0 12px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;color:#3f3f46;">
                Merci {{signerName}}. Votre signature du contrat <strong>{{documentTitle}}</strong> pour <strong>{{clientName}}</strong> a bien été enregistrée le {{signedAt}}.
              </p>
              <p style="margin:0;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;color:#3f3f46;">
                Vous trouverez en pièce jointe la version signée du document. Conservez-la pour vos archives.
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:20px 32px;background:#fafafa;border-top:1px solid #e4e4e7;">
              <p style="margin:0;font-size:12px;color:#a1a1aa;line-height:1.5;">
                Atome · atome.software
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
